  "page": "Morne (disambiguation)",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/index.php/Morne\" title=\"Morne\">Morne</a></b> is a ruined castle on the eastern shore of the island of Tarth.\n</p><p>Other usage includes:\n</p>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Galladon_of_Morne\" title=\"Galladon of Morne\">Galladon of Morne</a>, a legendary knight from Tarth</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morna_White_Mask\" title=\"Morna White Mask\">Morna White Mask</a>, a free folk leader</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morning\" title=\"Morning\">Morning</a>, a she-dragon ridden by Lady Rhaena Targaryen</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morningstar\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Morningstar\">Morningstar</a>, a weapon</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Morning_Tide\" title=\"Morning Tide\">Morning Tide</a>, a Velaryon warship</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Mountains_of_the_Morn\" title=\"Mountains of the Morn\">Mountains of the Morn</a>, a mountain range in far eastern Essos</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/On_a_Misty_Morn\" title=\"On a Misty Morn\">On a Misty Morn</a>, a song</li></ul>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404211530\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.003 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.004 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 4/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 0/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 0/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 1/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 0/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    0.000      1 -total\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:38951-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404211530 and revision id 326412\n -->\n",
